                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.001H87/13.</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Note.</hi>—Many protests were made to the President and to
                    the Secretary of State by Mexican consular and military officers of both the
                    Conventionist and the Constitutionalist factions against the landing of General
                    Huerta, most of them adding a request for his detention, in some instances with
                    the further request that he be delivered to Mexican authorities for trial.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
